# Studio naming (do not confuse repos)

| You mean | Use | Never call it |
|----------|-----|----------------|
| **Li World Studio** (product brand) | User-facing name in docs | A repo slug |
| **Editor / demo / mockups** | Repo **`studio-app`** | `li-world-studio`, `li-studio-app` |
| **`import studio`** | Repo **`studio`** | `li-studio` as published name |
| **`import studio.ai`** | Repo **`studio.ai`** | `li-studio-ai` |
| **`import world`** | Repo **`world`** | `li-world`; not the editor |

```bash
# Bootstrap application repo from lic (one-time)
./scripts/bootstrap-li-studio-app-repo.sh ../studio-app
```

**Packages:** `docs/ecosystem/package-import-naming.md` · **App:** `docs/ecosystem/studio-naming.md`
